<h1>Reset your password</h1>

<p>Hello {{firstName}},</p>

<p>We received a password reset request for your CYNA account. Click the button below to create a
  new password.</p>

<p style='text-align: center;'>
  <a href='{{resetLink}}' class='button'>Reset my password</a>
</p>

<div class='note'>
  <p>This link will expire in 1 hour. If you did not request this reset, ignore this email — your
    password will remain unchanged.</p>
</div>

<p>If the button doesn't work, copy and paste the following link into your browser:</p>
<p class='link-fallback'>{{resetLink}}</p>

<p>For security reasons, this link can only be used once.</p>